ly improves mobility</div></div><div class="benicontent"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/647085cadeace073b850ba3c/6476d40c6421f4871999060b_Vector.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="image-12"/><div class="text-block-26">creates the ability to exchange at precise times</div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-w-id="de2a7ca3-86da-0843-73fa-1a5ed8c596e8" style="opacity:0" class="certaintysec"><div class="columns-9 w-row"><div class="column-15 w-col w-col-6"><div class="benifitsdiv2"><h2 class="heading-22">Certainty</h2><div class="procontentwrap"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/647085cadeace073b850ba3c/6476d40c6421f4871999060b_Vector.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="image-13"/><div class="text-block-28">Transfers take place at precise, designated moments in time, and by creating a secure and accurate record​, we help ensure the right collateral gets to the right place at the right time. </div></div><div class="procontentwrap"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/647085cadeace073b850ba3c/6476d40c6421f4871999060b_Vector.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="image-13"/><div class="text-block-28">We remove uncertainty by reducing credit risk, operational risk and settlement failures​.</div></div></div></div><div class="w-col w-col-6"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/647085cadeace073b850ba3c/64773187692e55c571d6a69d_Mask%20group.png" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, (max-width: 1279px) 47vw, 48vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/647085cadeace073b850ba3c/64773187692e55c571d6a69d_Mask%20group-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/647085cadeace073b850ba3c/64773187692e55c571d6a69d_Mask%20group-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/647085cadeace073b850ba3c/64773187692e55c571d6a69d_Mask%20group.png 896w" alt=""/></div></div></div><div data-w-id="35c6b81f-8185-2039-e6d6-0788bc091d96" style="opacity:0" class="profitabilitysec"><div class="columns-10 w-row"><div class="w-col w-col-6"><im